565
00:40:24,510 --> 00:40:26,170
You should thank

566
00:40:27,030 --> 00:40:27,820
yourself the most.

567
00:40:41,070 --> 00:40:42,690
Ancestors of the Zhuang family,

568
00:40:44,480 --> 00:40:45,900
I wish for your blessing.

569
00:40:47,400 --> 00:40:48,940
Please bless Zhifu

570
00:40:48,960 --> 00:40:50,170
in his recovery.

571
00:40:51,630 --> 00:40:54,260
Please cure his mind.

572
00:40:55,190 --> 00:40:56,490
Everything that happens today

573
00:40:58,070 --> 00:41:00,420
