577
00:41:11,590 --> 00:41:13,170
Zhifu is innocent.

578
00:41:15,110 --> 00:41:16,820
He is the legitimate son of the Zhuang family.

579
00:41:19,710 --> 00:41:22,260
If he can recover soon,

580
00:41:23,760 --> 00:41:25,780
he will regain the Marquis's favor.

581
00:41:26,630 --> 00:41:29,980
Ancestors, please bless my son.

582
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:48,460
My lady.

583
00:42:05,340 --> 00:42:07,020
[Late wife Shen Wan's tablet]

584
00:42:11,940 --> 00:42:14,220
[Erected by Zhuang Luyin]

585
00:42:14,590 --> 00:42:16,260
Why is this hag's memorial tablet

586
00:42:17,320 --> 00:42:18,650
placed here?

587
00:42:20,590 --> 00:42:21,260
Someone!

588
00:42:21,710 --> 00:42:22,380
Someone!

589
00:42:23,280 --> 00:42:24,490
